@startuml GamificationBadges
left to right direction

actor "Administrator" as admin
actor "Instructor" as instructor
actor "Student" as student
actor "System" as system
actor "External Verifier" as external_verifier

rectangle "Gamification & Badges System" {
  usecase "Create Badge" as UC2101
  usecase "Design Image" as design_image
  usecase "Set Criteria" as UC2102
  usecase "Validate Conditions" as validate_conditions
  usecase "Award Badge" as UC2103
  usecase "Log Achievement" as log_achievement
  usecase "Display Badges" as UC2104
  usecase "Fetch Badge Data" as fetch_badge_data
  usecase "Export Badge" as UC2105
  usecase "Verify Badge" as verify_badge
  usecase "Manage Badge Types" as UC2106
}

' Actor Associations
admin --> UC2101 : **Association**
instructor --> UC2101 : **Association**
admin --> UC2102 : **Association**
instructor --> UC2102 : **Association**
system --> UC2103 : **Association**
student --> UC2104 : **Association**
external_verifier --> verify_badge : **Association**

' Use Case Relationships
UC2101 ..> design_image : **<<include>>**
UC2102 ..> validate_conditions : **<<include>>**
UC2103 ..> log_achievement : **<<include>>**
UC2104 ..> fetch_badge_data : **<<include>>**
UC2105 ..> UC2104 : **<<extend>>**

@enduml